 importance of\nexploiting informative external information. The code and dataset are both\navailable at https://github.com/HumaticsLAB/GTM-Transformer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Sep 2021 20:15:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2021 07:17:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 8 Oct 2021 09:33:18 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 26 Oct 2021 07:47:50 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 15 Sep 2022 12:06:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-16"}
