y constrain the\nkinematic and flavor dependence of nuclear effects in hadron production,\nprobing an unexplored kinematic region. They will help to reveal how the\nnucleus reacts to a fast quark, thereby shedding light on its color structure,\ntransport properties, and on the mechanisms of the hadronization process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Sep 2021 04:13:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 00:29:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-17"}
