on Transformer, with minimal accuracy drops\n(0.1-0.3%) on ImageNet. Code release: https://github.com/changlin31/DS-Net\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Sep 2021 09:57:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-22"}
