uantum mechanical triple-well-potential, which accurately\nrepresents the anti-phase synchronization of apical oxygens displacements and\nlattice-assisted charge transfer to the $CuO_2$ plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Sep 2021 15:42:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jan 2023 14:35:36 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2023 13:10:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-03"}
